model
*****


Description
===========

Models are mathematical representations of the relationships between
data. Models are represented by their associated metadata and
artifacts.


Available Commands
==================

* change-compartment

* create

* create-model-artifact

* create-model-provenance

* deactivate

* delete

* get

* get-artifact-content

* get-model-provenance

* head-model-artifact

* list

* update
